And under it add this

[code=cmf]} else if (token.equals("character-startersfail")) {
startersfail = Integer.parseInt(token2);[/code]

Then search for

[code=cmf]characterfile.write("character-tz = ", 0, 15);[/code]

And under it add this

[code=cmf]characterfile.write("character-startersfail = ", 0, 25);
characterfile.write(Integer.toString(startersfail), 0, Integer.toString(startersfail).length());
characterfile.newLine();[/code]

